## What This Module Does

This module ports the "Depth Blur" effect from VJlive-2. It implements a cinematic, optical-style Depth of Field (DoF) effect using real depth camera data. It simulates real lens optics including adjustable focal planes, bokeh shape simulation, chromatic fringing, and optional tilt-shift modes.

---

## What It Does NOT Do

- It does NOT simply run a generic Gaussian blur. It uses a multi-tap sampling method (Poisson or Disc sampling) to simulate optical bokeh.
- It does NOT rely on motion estimation.

